"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"240 幾時入好"},{"pid":"7fbdb6c80eb6c72337cc615f16dc0cabf1434e56","tid":526304,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"6088"},{"pid":"2a7563f84763773421277206009089f4f2494507","tid":526304,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dcc331a07894e7e9c73ef2a589631c65a28539c","tid":526304,"uid":77186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"240 幾時入好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"我估佢三月出業績會派3仙至三仙半息<br />\n上年二月出完盈喜由3毫升咗上6毫<br />\n唔知今年仲有無盈喜出呢"},{"pid":"9d7f75b3bf2c093fe5386c7a37d2bcd7499147fb","tid":526304,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bbcd9bc3da93641499ab7e7eea49764b85c7ffa","tid":526304,"uid":40932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2681024e1da239deb873f753c5767dc9059de11b","tid":526304,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84559ff637f4d80d3d8a93c1efdc83c7d1ee6028","tid":526304,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"2382同2018都係由幾蚊升起，歡迎討論一下細價潛力股<br />\n雖然個市係咁升，不過我相信市場上仲有啲股票係被人遺忘咗/有待發掘<br />\n希望大家討論時列出原因同分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，小弟近排睇中咗 0240 利基集團<br />\n<br />\n1. 盈利及派息增長<br />\n近幾年盈利增長都唔錯，派息亦一直加<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/211637_beae0e008204bddd1934eca5e3208e90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F211637_beae0e008204bddd1934eca5e3208e90.jpg&h=632dcd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/211702_5cab824f264a05f8a693fab8268b0478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F211702_5cab824f264a05f8a693fab8268b0478.jpg&h=79baff6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信管理層有一定實力<br />\n<br />\n2. PE 及 PB 低，息高<br />\n現價PE 4.8, PB1.3; 現價都有4里幾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/211835_98fad66ed9dba5a970f66a67ec2a045f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F211835_98fad66ed9dba5a970f66a67ec2a045f.jpg&h=36e5305a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果4月佢派3仙，股價有望升上6毫半<br />\n<br />\n3. 母公司增持<br />\n上年年中母公司惠記增持股份，應該都睇好公司前景<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 公司前景<br />\n年中報告話佢尚有大約一百億contract 喺手<br />\n不過剩係近哩2個月都接多咗大約70億contract，嚟緊哩幾年盈利應該有一定保證<br />\n<br />\nSt. Paul 醫院重建，3億<br />\n東涌東新市鎮填海67億， 利基佔5成，大概33億<br />\n中九龍幹線50億，利基佔6成，大概30億<br />\n<br />\n2年前同佢做鑽石山站嘅contractor 走咗佬，240都被洗倉，不過後來佢獨力完成咗單contract, 實力都有返咁上下<br />\n<br />\n加上佢之前接到三跑填海工程，又無乜香港以外嘅項目，係本土老牌公司<br />\n議事規則修改咗，正苦嚟緊又係咁推工程.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上係學術討論，無叫你買；投資涉及風險，證券價格有時會大幅波動，價格可升亦可跌，更可變.得毫無價值。投資未必一定能夠賺取利潤，反而可能會招致損失，往績數字並非. 未來表現的指標。投資前應先閱讀有關產品的發售文件、財務及相關的風險聲明</span><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家又有無其它潛力股呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"睇番10年前0.9已經知唔洗睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"我都係見佢近幾年開始派息，仲年年加<br />\ncut 哂香港以外蝕錢嘅業務，工程又越接越大，所以先考慮"},{"pid":"62e4d40a89a5053bf430a0b8288d2b577cd886b7","tid":526304,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"工程公司就算喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0730f0ac7d4f15706618dc4c1e7fded646cd861d","tid":526304,"uid":131153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"點睇1979呢幾年有盈利有增長有股息 但都跌到落52週低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc836fc781996ef076e6214770b82ea319912d4","tid":526304,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"禽日8043大家執左幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":